Package grafioschtrader.repository

Interface GTNetExchangeJpaRepositoryCustom

All Known Subinterfaces:
GTNetExchangeJpaRepository
All Known Implementing Classes:
GTNetExchangeJpaRepositoryImpl
public interface GTNetExchangeJpaRepositoryCustom
Custom repository interface for GTNetExchange operations not covered by Spring Data JPA. Provides methods for:
  • Retrieving securities with their GTNetExchange configurations
  • Retrieving currency pairs with their GTNetExchange configurations
  • Batch updating multiple GTNetExchange entries
  • Adding new securities/currency pairs to the exchange configuration
  • Retrieving supplier details for expandable row display

    • batchUpdate

      List<GTNetExchange> batchUpdate(List<GTNetExchange> exchanges)
      Batch updates multiple GTNetExchange entries. Only updates entries that have actually changed (dirty check).
      Parameters:
      exchanges - list of GTNetExchange entities to update
      Returns:
      list of updated GTNetExchange entities

    • addSecurity

      GTNetExchange addSecurity(Integer idSecuritycurrency)
      Adds a new security to the GTNetExchange configuration. Creates a new GTNetExchange entry with all boolean fields set to false.
      Parameters:
      idSecuritycurrency - the ID of the security to add
      Returns:
      the newly created GTNetExchange entry
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the security doesn't exist or is already configured

    • addCurrencypair

      GTNetExchange addCurrencypair(Integer idSecuritycurrency)
      Adds a new currency pair to the GTNetExchange configuration. Creates a new GTNetExchange entry with all boolean fields set to false.
      Parameters:
      idSecuritycurrency - the ID of the currency pair to add
      Returns:
      the newly created GTNetExchange entry
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the currency pair doesn't exist or is already configured

    • getSupplierDetails

      List<GTNetSupplierWithDetails> getSupplierDetails(Integer idSecuritycurrency)
      Retrieves supplier details for a given security or currency pair. Used for expandable row display to show which remote suppliers can provide price data for this instrument.
      Parameters:
      idSecuritycurrency - the ID of the security or currency pair
      Returns:
      DTO containing GTNetSupplier header and list of GTNetSupplierDetail entries
